description: Chef Richard is taking his lovely truck all over Bend, Oregon and delighting the hungry locals with his delicious organic and vegan variety of New South American cuisine, with a perfect touch of French-inspired Pacific Northwest flair. Everything from A Broken Angel is made with local sustainable ingredients, and you can taste the freshness and quality in every scrumptious bite. His seasonal selection of sandwiches, soups, salads, burritos, and more all make for the perfect meal, whether you’re just plain ready to eat, or wish to share the experience with all your friends and family at your next event.
name: A Broken Angel
